26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_fifo_gpfifonv50.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:31 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "channv50.h"
30
31#include <core/client.h>
32#include <core/ramht.h>
33
34#include <nvif/class.h>
35#include <nvif/unpack.h>
36
37static int
38nv50_fifo_gpfifo_new(struct nvkm_fifo *base, const struct nvkm_oclass *oclass,
39 void *data, u32 size, struct nvkm_object **pobject)
40{
41 struct nvkm_object *parent = oclass->parent;
42 union {
43 struct nv50_channel_gpfifo_v0 v0;
44 } *args = data;
45 struct nv50_fifo *fifo = nv50_fifo(base);
46 struct nv50_fifo_chan *chan;
47 u64 ioffset, ilength;
48 int ret;
49
50 nvif_ioctl(parent, "create channel gpfifo size %d\n", size);
51 if (nvif_unpack(args->v0, 0, 0, false)) {
52 nvif_ioctl(parent, "create channel gpfifo vers %d vm %"PRIx64" "
53 "pushbuf %"PRIx64" ioffset %016"PRIx64" "
54 "ilength %08x\n",
55 args->v0.version, args->v0.vm, args->v0.pushbuf,
56 args->v0.ioffset, args->v0.ilength);
57 if (!args->v0.pushbuf)
58 return -EINVAL;
59 } else
60 return ret;
61
62 if (!(chan = kzalloc(sizeof(*chan), GFP_KERNEL)))
63 return -ENOMEM;
64 *pobject = &chan->base.object;
65
66 ret = nv50_fifo_chan_ctor(fifo, args->v0.vm, args->v0.pushbuf,
67 oclass, chan);
68 if (ret)
69 return ret;
70
71 args->v0.chid = chan->base.chid;
72 ioffset = args->v0.ioffset;
73 ilength = order_base_2(args->v0.ilength / 8);
74
75 nvkm_kmap(chan->ramfc);
76 nvkm_wo32(chan->ramfc, 0x3c, 0x403f6078);
77 nvkm_wo32(chan->ramfc, 0x44, 0x01003fff);
78 nvkm_wo32(chan->ramfc, 0x48, chan->base.push->node->offset >> 4);
79 nvkm_wo32(chan->ramfc, 0x50, lower_32_bits(ioffset));
80 nvkm_wo32(chan->ramfc, 0x54, upper_32_bits(ioffset) | (ilength << 16));
81 nvkm_wo32(chan->ramfc, 0x60, 0x7fffffff);
82 nvkm_wo32(chan->ramfc, 0x78, 0x00000000);
83 nvkm_wo32(chan->ramfc, 0x7c, 0x30000001);
84 nvkm_wo32(chan->ramfc, 0x80, ((chan->ramht->bits - 9) << 27) |
85 (4 << 24) /* SEARCH_FULL */ |
86 (chan->ramht->gpuobj->node->offset >> 4));
87 nvkm_done(chan->ramfc);
88 return 0;
89}
90
91const struct nvkm_fifo_chan_oclass
92nv50_fifo_gpfifo_oclass = {
93 .base.oclass = NV50_CHANNEL_GPFIFO,
94 .base.minver = 0,
95 .base.maxver = 0,
96 .ctor = nv50_fifo_gpfifo_new,
97};
